## Deliver the BEAM's stdin to the app (StdinReader) instead of an Erlang
## shell — required for the MCP stdio transport. Mirrors the `-noshell`
## that `mix run --no-halt` uses.
-noshell

## Do not attempt to read the boot script's own input as Erlang terms.
+Bd

## Reasonable defaults for a small, long-lived stdio service.
+K true
